Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: San Jose, California
Description: This is where I grew up.  I always enjoy coming back home because this is where I made many good friends and wonderful memories.  San Jose has a lot of restaurants that serve food from many different cultures.  My favorite thing to do when I come home is to try new restaurants with my friends and family.

Name: Sacramento, California
Description: I have been here on two separate occasions, and I have fond memories of both trips, so this is one of my favorite places.  My first trip here was a 3 day school field trip where I competed for my school's HOSA (Health Occupations Students of America).  I had a great time during this trip because I was able to meet students from all over California.  The second time I came here was for a trip with my best friend.  It was a calming trip where we just tried different restaurants and relaxed at the hotel.  This trip was a wonderful break from school and work obligation.

Name: Disneyland
Description: This is also a place that I have fond memories of because I have traveled here with my friends and family to go to Disneyland.  I also liked trying the restaurants here.

Name: Honolulu, Hawaii
Description: I have left California two times in my entire life, and this place is where I went to for one of those visits.  My sister had a volleyball tournament in Hawaii, so my mother and I took this opportunity to come to Hawaii as well.  I really enjoyed going to the beaches and wandering the marketplaces in Hawaii.

Name: Vietnam
Description: This is the country that my family is from.  My parents moved to the US before I was born and worked hard to create a home that they can raise me and my sister in.  I have traveled here once with my family, but I was only six years old so I do not remember much from this trip.  I hope to travel here in the future.

Name: Santa Cruz Beach Boardwalk
Description: Going to the Santa Cruz Beach Boardwalk is something that I do at least once every summer.  I go with my family.  Although the beach is normally very crowded, I still find this an enjoyable summer experience because I am having a good time with my family.

Name: San Francisco, California
Description: This is a place that I often go to for day trips with my friends and family.  It is far enough from San Jose (where I am from) that it feels like we are taking a mini vacation, but close enough that we can make it back home when we are done with enjoying the city.
